Élodie Bouchez https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%89lodie_Bouchez 0 Élodie Bouchez-Bangalter is a French actress. She is known for her role as Renée Rienne on the fifth and final season of the television show Alias and for playing Maïté Alvarez in the film Wild Reeds.
